---
title: Honey-Roasted Feta (v) with Garlicky Lentils and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: If you’ve never honey-roasted your feta before, you’re about to take your taste buds into the taste stratosphere. Combining golden, creamy feta with lemony garlic lentils, earthy sweet potatoes, peppery rocket and fresh pomegranate seeds is a flavour combination you’re going to love, and one you’ll be creating time and time again. You can thank us later.
